      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 44-49.</p><p>Kensei Technique</p><p>At 25th level, you learn one Kensei Technique–a more powerful version of a Mythical Technique. Kensei Techniques follow the same rules as Mythical Techniques, as detailed in Part III, with one exception: once you use a Kensei Technique, you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
